{
  "stem": "12051.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[SIGHS] The following weeks, most probably, the, the, the Polish family found out that those parents were killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We saw those children going around by the camp, begging for a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because they threw them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a little boy and a little girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I don't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But their name was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Hoffmann. ?] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] After the doctor was killed, then all her helpers, also doctors-- I couldn't go out for-- to the lavatory, which was a outhouse, for weeks.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because the pieces of brain and then skull was lying out on the field, which they never buried.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the shock-- we were friends with those people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Every inmate was your relative because you had nobody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you tried to support-- like a support group, you tried to talk to each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We will survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We will do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We will-- if you lost your sense of humor, you had lost everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we were entertaining each other while we were sitting on the barracks killing the lice.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were talking to each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I'm inviting you for coffee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I made good cheesecake.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It sounds ridiculous today.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But that was maybe what kept us going, that you had the will to hope that this is not the end of everything, that we will be able to continue.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you couldn't give up because there was nothing that you could kill yourself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A pencil was immediate death sentence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You used the-- in order to eat, to get that wonderful soup that you got that day, you had an old can that somebody threw out, or whatever, that you found, or a dish, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you had no knives, no forks, no-- you, you lived like an animal.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
